arts.ttl: Bahoya, Uzun provide Eintracht Frankfurt with perfect start against Werder Bremen
arts.sum: Eintracht Frankfurt kicked off their Bundesliga season in style after Jean-Mattéo Bahoya and Can Uzun starred to down visiting Werder Bremen. Fresh from equalling their best-ever Bundesliga finish last season, Eintracht enjoyed a statement win at the start of 2025/26 as Dino Toppmöller's men posted an impressive win with Bahoya and Uzun to the fore against Werder.

arts.ttl: Eintracht Frankfurt vs. SV Werder Bremen preview: Adler look for another strong start
arts.sum: Eintracht Frankfurt and SV Werder Bremen begin their 2025/26 Bundesliga campaigns on Saturday, 15:30 CET at Deutsche Bank Park.
